2: Spirit of The Water; Camel; Moonmadness; 1976
3: Sea of Tranquility; Gazpacho; Bravo; 2003
4: Living in the Past; Jethro Tull; Living in the Past; 1969
5: Eclipse; Pink Floyd; The Dark Side Of The Moon; 1973
6: Moonwalk; Moon Safari; Blomljud ; 2008
7: The Red Moon; Leviathan; Bee Yourself; 1990
8: Dancing With The Moonlit Knight; Genesis; Selling England By The Pound; 1973
9: Ticket To The Moon; Electric Light Orchestra; Time; 1981

